                    <span>The book is terrific but I found a virus on the CD. I notified Mr. Kabir but it is the publisher's responsibility and they did not provide an email address for complaints.<P>virus is the Unix PSite virus and it is in the VetesCan-8-9-200.tar.gz file.<P>Buyer beware!</span>
                  
              
